\mathcal{S}
S\in \mathcal{S} \Leftrightarrow \exists j\in I \ \ \exists O\in \tau_j \ \ \forall i \in I\setminus \{j\}: Y_i=X_i \textrm{ and } Y_j=O,
S=\{f:I\rightarrow \cup_{i\in I} X_i \ | \ \exists i\in I \ \ \exists O\in \tau_i: f(i)\in O  \}.
